*Dužnik duguje*, (The debtor owes).

*Ona duguje svojoj majci*, (She owes her mother).

*Duguješ mi mnogo*, (You owe me a lot).

*Oni duguju svoju poštovanje*, (They owe their respect).

*Mi dugujemo da se pridržavamo zakona*, (We owe it to abide by the law).

*Oni duguju jedni drugima*, (They owe each other).

*Ti duguješ ispriku*, (You owe an apology).

*Oni duguju poštovanje svojoj zemlji*, (They owe respect to their country).